oblem','That\'s fantastic that you want to become a DevOps engineer! Here’s a positive and encouraging roadmap to help you on your journey:\n\n**Step 1: Linux Fundamentals**\nStart with these great courses to build a solid foundation in Linux:\n- **Linux for Cloud & DevOps Engineers**: Perfect for beginners! [Check it out here](https://www.udemy.com/course/valaxy-linux/).\n- **Linux for Beginners**: A comprehensive course for all levels! [Explore it here](https://www.udemy.com/course/linuxforbeginners/).\n- **Linux Administration & Command Line for Beginners**: A great way to get hands-on experience! [Learn more here](https://www.udemy.com/course/introduction-to-linux-centos-7/).\n- **CompTIA Linux+ Exam Practice Tests**: Test your knowledge as you learn! [Find it here](https://www.udemy.com/course/comptia-linux-xk0-005-exam-practice-tests/).\n- **Linux Command Line Basics**: Essential skills for any DevOps engineer! [Start learning here](https://www.udemy.com/course/linux-command-line-volume1/).\n\n**Step 2: Monitoring and Logging**\nNext, dive into monitoring and logging with these courses:\n- **Monitoring and Maintaining GenAI Systems**: A fascinating look at AI systems! [Join here](https://www.udemy.com/course/monitoring-and-maintaining-genai-systems-generative-ai/).\n- **Nagios: Mastering Monitoring and Management**: Gain valuable skills in system monitoring! [Check it out here](https://www.udemy.com/course/nagios-mastering-monitoring-and-management/).\n- **Monitoring and Evaluation**: Learn the importance of evaluation in development! [Explore it here](https://www.udemy.com/course/monitoring-and-evaluation/).\n- **Sound the Alarm: Detection and Response**: A crucial course for cybersecurity! [Learn more here](https://www.coursera.org/learn/detection-and-response).\n- **AWS Cloud Practitioner Essentials**: A great introduction to cloud computing! [Start here](https://www.coursera.org/learn/aws-cloud-practitioner-essentials).\n\n**Step 3: Version Control with Git**\nMaster version control with these fantastic resources:\n- **Introduction to Git and GitHub**: A beginner-friendly course! [Join here](https://www.coursera.org/learn/introduction-git-github).\n- **Git Complete**: A step-by-step guide to mastering Git! [Check it out here](https://www.udemy.com/course/git-complete/).\n- **Basic Git and GitHub - Essentials**: Perfect for all levels! [Explore it here](https://www.udemy.com/course/basic-git-and-github/).\n- **Git & GitHub - The Practical Guide**: Hands-on learning for developers! [Learn more here](https://www.udemy.com/course/git-github-practical-guide/).\n- **Version Control**: A great introduction to software development tools! [Start learning here](https://www.coursera.org/learn/introduction-to-version-control).\n\n**Step 4: Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment (CI/CD)**\nGet ready for CI/CD with these engaging courses:\n- **DevOps, CI/CD for Beginners**: A fantastic starting point! [Join here](https://www.udemy.com/course/ci-cd-devops/).\n- **Docker for Developers and DevOps**: Learn about containerization! [Check it out here](https://www.udemy.com/course/docker-for-developers/).\n- **Build+Deploy+Test with Jenkins 2.0**: A hands-on approach to CI/CD! [Explore it here](https://www.udemy.com/course/working-with-jenkins/).\n- **DevOps Project 1 - CI/CD with Git Jenkins Ansible Kubernetes**: A comprehensive project to apply your skills! [Learn more here](https://www.udemy.com/course/valaxy-devops/).\n- **DevOps and AI on AWS**: Combine DevOps with AI! [Start here](https://www.coursera.org/specializations/devops-ai-aws).\n\n**Step 5: Infrastructure as Code (IaC)**\nFinally, explore Infrastructure as Code with these excellent courses:\n- **DevOps and AI on AWS**: A great way to integrate cloud computing! [Join here](https://www.coursera.org/specializations/devops-ai-aws).\n- **Terraform on AWS with SRE & IaC DevOps**: Real-world demos to enhance your learning! [Check it out here](https://www.udemy.com/course/terraform-on-aws-with-sre-iac-devops-real-world-demos/).\n- **Terraform for Beginners using GCP**: Hands-on experience with Google Cloud! [Explore it here](https://www.udemy.com/course/terraform-for-beginners-using-google-cloud/).\n- **Terraform for AWS - Beginner to Expert**: A comprehensive course for all levels! [Learn more here](https://www.udemy.com/course/terraform-fast-track/).\n- **Terraform on Azure**: Expand your skills to Azure! [Start here](https://www.udemy.com/course/terraform-on-azure/).\n\nRemember, every step you take brings you closer to your goal! Embrace the learning process, and don\'t hesitate to reach out for support along the way. You\'ve got this!','roadmap','2025-05-26 13:21:02','2025-05-26 13:21:36',0,NULL,'1caf4710-6c7d-481d-bc75-46553a820d1','5e779b7d-0052-4dce-8066-4c3cb7b32898','devops engineer','beginner',5,NULL),('fff6656c-9a2b-4487-851e-359818752d55','...',NULL,NULL,'2025-06-25 07:19:57',NULL,0,NULL,'0dece535-bec3-41c0-b725-83f678365926','24f119cf-36c3-4340-a9dd-35c00bab7625',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
